item.title: Mobile Art from Wooster Collective
item.description: Wooster Collective has a cool new service that sends great urban art pieces to your phone. The images are $1.99, and can be installed directly as wallpaper (depending on phone model), or saved. Proceeds benefit Keep a Child Alive.Link
